02:21.860 --> 02:24.500
I can't believe she's gone.

02:24.500 --> 02:26.000
- What about Abigail?

02:26.000 --> 02:28.000
- I saw her
before the game started.

02:28.000 --> 02:29.600
- You heard the gunshot?

