real life or extreme situations

03:28.560 --> 03:30.960
using physical and
mental dexterity.

03:30.960 --> 03:32.730
- This one was a prison break.

03:32.730 --> 03:34.000
- That's ironic.

03:34.000 --> 03:35.570
- Each kid had to find
his partner,

03:35.570 --> 03:36.900
