There wasn't a single drop
of her DNA at the crime scene.

04:13.770 --> 04:15.970
The prosecutor kept her
locked up for three years

04:15.980 --> 04:18.779
before starting her trial.

04:18.779 --> 04:21.050
I was kind of obsessed
with the case.

04:21.050 --> 04:24.050
My point is maybe
it's too early to convict her.

04:24.050 --> 04:26.850
- I wouldn't rely on
the TV movie.

04:26.850 --> 04:30.860
- I read two books,
and the trial transcripts.

04:30.860 --> 04:33.990
