07:30.900 --> 07:32.540
- Follow him?

07:32.540 --> 07:34.640
- I don't think
those tampons are for mom.

07:37.010 --> 07:38.580
- You think she's guilty?

07:38.580 --> 07:40.110
- Which murder
are we talking about?

07:40.110 --> 07:42.310
- He's picking up the pace.

07:42.320 --> 07:44.050
She was 18 when
she went to Madrid.

07:44.050 --> 07:45.850
She didn't speak the language.
For all we know,

07:45.850 --> 07:47.320
