07:47.320 --> 07:49.320
- She's hot so she's innocent.

07:49.320 --> 07:51.620
- Oh, come on, I didn't say
I want to marry the girl.

08:12.310 --> 08:14.210
- Who the hell is that?

08:14.210 --> 08:16.280
- Gun!

