08:40.110 --> 08:41.270
- Out of my way, bro-meo.

08:41.270 --> 08:42.640
- Ah!

08:42.640 --> 08:43.940
- No, please, please, please!

08:43.940 --> 08:45.110
No, no!

08:45.110 --> 08:46.380
- Let go of the girl!

08:46.380 --> 08:48.150
- Ah, come on, man!

08:48.150 --> 08:49.210
- Turn around!

08:49.220 --> 08:50.880
- I found her first.

08:50.880 --> 08:53.120
We can work a deal.
Who sent you?

08:53.120 --> 08:55.050
- State's attorney's office.

08:55.050 --> 08:56.950
Your turn.
- Spain.

08:56.960 --> 08:59.360
I'm a bounty hunter.

08:59.360 --> 09:01.990
Let me have her and
I'll cut you in on my action.

09:02.000 --> 09:03.860
How's ten percent?
