09:03.860 --> 09:06.860
Once a pig, always...

09:06.870 --> 09:08.200
All right, man! Shove off, man!

09:08.200 --> 09:09.270
- Todd. Scram.

09:09.270 --> 09:10.670
- I've got ID!

09:10.670 --> 09:12.400
- Abigail,
you're coming with us.

09:12.410 --> 09:14.270
- Following her since Madrid.
- Let me see your ID!

09:14.270 --> 09:15.970
- I've got ID in my pocket.
- Get up!

09:20.680 --> 09:23.250
- Do you go to church?

09:23.250 --> 09:25.250
I used to go...

09:25.250 --> 09:28.150
Prison is the opposite.

09:28.150 --> 09:29.420
Church...

09:29.420 --> 09:32.420
It lifts your mind upwards...

09:32.430 --> 09:35.430
To a place...
I don't know...

09:35.430 --> 09:39.360
Beyond the reaches of your soul.

09:39.370 --> 09:42.370
But prison...

09:42.370 --> 09:44.140
It pushes you down.

09:44.140 --> 09:46.040
- Is that why you ran away?

09:46.040 --> 09:48.910
You don't want to go back?
- Maybe I'm just psycho!

09:48.910 --> 09:50.440
