by association.

12:43.380 --> 12:44.850
- That's sick.

12:44.850 --> 12:46.950
- Celeb central.

12:50.520 --> 12:53.120
- This picture was taken
in the escape room.

12:53.130 --> 12:54.960
Find out who sold it
to celeb central,

12:54.960 --> 12:56.130
and see if there are any more.

12:56.130 --> 12:58.360
- Yeah.

13:00.100 --> 13:01.530
- Okay, guys.

13:01.530 --> 13:03.430
I got a double sawbuck

13:03.440 --> 13:06.440
for anyone who can tell me
who shot this photo.

13:06.440 --> 13:08.370
- Nobody here, that's for sure.

13:08.370 --> 13:10.110
That cover was mine.

13:10.110 --> 13:12.880
That punk ass kid comes in
like he's Annie leibovitz

13:12.880 --> 13:14.880
and I end up on page 15.

13:14.880 --> 13:16.510
Now I'm out here with
these knuckleheads,

13:16.520 --> 13:18.520
freezing my tush off,
trying to get pictures of

13:18.520 --> 13:20.990
Selena swapping spit
