her own vomit

13:44.980 --> 13:46.480
at the sigma phi party.

13:46.480 --> 13:48.080
Guess who still
gets to attend ccu?

13:48.080 --> 13:50.480
- How much did celeb central
pay you for this?

13:50.480 --> 13:52.120
- What are you, the IRS?

13:52.120 --> 13:54.150
- We just want to know
if you have any more.

